<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Parallel Plays: Multiple Words in One Turn</h2>

<p>Another route to 50+ is forming multiple words simultaneously. By playing parallel to an existing word, every new letter forms a 2-letter crossword — and each scores independently.</p>

